<p>John and Dave head into this last Premium episode of April talking about managing your Mac&rsquo;s menubar, why some boot disks can boot all Macs &mdash; and why some can&rsquo;t, changing your default Mail client, playing specific movies with specific apps, and lots, lots more! Subscribe today, support your two favorite geeks, and enjoy!</p>
